{"tid":84272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油麻地男子墮樓　倒臥馬路重傷亡","createTime":"2017-01-17T11:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T12:09:58.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"811ce7e99a70262ef8628906d85d3d3c26fb71c1","tid":84272,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:53:49.000Z","msg":"油麻地文明里，早上11時許，一名男子被人發現由高處墮下，昏迷倒臥於文明里馬路上。救護員接報到場，將事主送院搶救，最終證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX9piSuXnnipRXygasfXDC2zBsxczFvQegqzFkPQwxKxd?filename=56uQWze.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F56uQWze.jpg&h=7ec02256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n死者年約55歲，警方調查後，相信他由彌敦道497A號麗星大廈18樓天台墮下，先壓中一樓賓館外牆招牌，再壓中一輛客貨車車尾反彈跌在地上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170117/s00001/1484633357180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170117%2Fs00001%2F1484633357180&d=2j%2F0E%2FhdxIz%2F47vfqW8je3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=b92a6cef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170117%2Fs00001%2F1484633357180&h=6d398aa1\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170117/s00001/1484633357180</a><br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線<br />\n<br />\n機構：電話<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線：2382 0000<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞防止自殺會：2389 2222<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署：2343 2255<br />\n<br />\n明愛向晴軒：18288"},{"pid":"60fdc86bb5c823ff2dd69553b77d6a14fb1ff5bf","tid":84272,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:54:21.000Z","msg":"阿門～"},{"pid":"bd9f0c1bd3dd1a01942c99c808bf0697147aff25","tid":84272,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:58:32.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"9c771fec91294b75c1e00b36ca455fc589442679","tid":84272,"uid":73737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:02:36.000Z","msg":"R.I.P"